  "body": "[This PR](https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/pull/596) was just merged which adds an event that gets emitted when a relayed message reverts.\r\n\r\nWould be nice to be able to pick up this event using the watcher to see information about how the message reverted, etc.\r\n\r\nShould we add a new method for getting a reverted relay message or just detect the fail event in the existing `getL2TransactionReceipt` method?",
