    "body": "This was silently fixed in https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/pull/937\r\n\r\nForgot about this issue. Please note that the watcher doesn't distinguish between failed and successful messages. For L1 => L2 messages you can distinguish based on the transaction receipt (status == 0 -> failed message). If you think it'd be worth distinguishing the two I'd recommend opening another issue with your preferred interface. Ty!!!",
